Vaseline® Lip Therapy® Rosy Lips Tin has been clinically proven to help heal dry lips, and it gives your lips a natural, rosy shine. This tinted lip balm has a non-sticky formula that melts into lips to lock in moisture while enhancing your lip color. Our Vaseline® lip balm tins are convenient, so you can take them with you in your bag, purse, or pocket, and moisturize whenever your lips feel dry.
Natural, Rosy Shine
When you have dry lips, the last thing you want is to make them worse. Vaseline Lip Therapy® Rosy Lips truly moisturizes while also bringing out lips' natural rosy tones. This tinted lip moisturizer provides a glossy look with a hint of pink – and you'll love the scent that has elements of rose, vanilla, and red berry.
Made with the Original Wonder Jelly
Like all Vaseline® lip products, this formula is made with pure Vaseline® Jelly that has been protecting and helping to heal dry skin since 1870. This product brings you the dry skin healing benefits of our original Jelly in a formula custom designed for lips, so Vaseline Lip Therapy® Rosy Lips is a lip balm you can trust.
Locks in Moisture
The top protective layer of skin on your lips is thinner than on the rest of your body, and can be more susceptible to dryness. Vaseline® Rosy Lips tin is a moisturizing lip balm that penetrates into lips rather than simply sitting on the surface. The formula locks in moisture to support your lips' natural recovery from dryness.

description:
The JAPONESQUE® Velvet Touch Pedicure Kit pampers feet to polished perfection.
Kit Includes:
Velvet Touch Dual Surfaced Foot Smoother: Micro-file polishes away tough calluses while emery buffing side smooths to reveal soft supple skin. Innovative soft touch finish and ergonomic design offers extra control and comfort in the palm of your hand.
Washable Salon Board: Medium grit, padded surface is ideal for shaping nails.
Straight Edge Toenail Clipper: Straight edge blades neatly clip and trim nails and help prevent ingrown toenails.

Directions for use: Soak feet in warm water to soften skin and pat dry. Using micro-file side of the Dual Surfaced Foot Smoother, gently slide across feet and heels to remove thin layers of dead skin. Use emery buffing surface to smooth out any rough remaining skin. Position toenails in clipper. Squeeze handles and clip to achieve desired length. Use the washable salon board to file from corner of nail to center, in one direction only. Care Instructions: Dual Surfaced Foot Smoother: Open compartment behind micro-file to empty skin shavings after each use. Wash micro-file surface in hot soapy water and rinse well.
Washable Salon Board: Clean with warm, soapy water. Replace when worn.
Straight Edge Toenail Clipper: Use cotton pad with alcohol to clean after use.
Store kit in cool, dry place. Warning: Micro-file surface and blades are extremely sharp. Keep out of reach of children. For use on hard skin on feet only. Stop if skin becomes sore or inflamed. Use only on dry skin. Do not use on broken or sore skin. This product is not suitable for people with diabetes or those with poor blood circulation.
title: JAPONESQUE Velvet Touch Pedicure Kit

bullets: Dual Surfaced Foot Smoother, Washable Salon Board and Straight Edge Toenail Clipper
Innovative soft touch finish for extra control and comfort
